              (11 < 3 · 4) ∧ (4 ≤ i) 
            =⟨ Assumption `i ≥ 4` ⟩
              (11 < 3 · 4) ∧ true 
            =⟨ Fact `11 < 3 · 4` ⟩
              true ∧ true 
            =⟨ “Idempotency of ∧” ⟩ 
              true
          Case `i < 4`:
              ¬ (11 = 3 · i)
            ⇐⟨ “Symmetry of =”, “Irreflexivity of <” ⟩
              (3 · i < 11)
            ⇐⟨ “Transitivity of ≤ with <” ⟩
              3 · i ≤ 3 · 3 ∧ 3 · 3 < 11
