              3 · i ≤ 3 · 3 ∧ true
            =⟨ “Monotonicity of ·” with Fact `0 < 3` ⟩
              i ≤ 3 ∧ true
            =⟨ “Less than successor” ⟩
              i < 3 + 1 ∧ true
            =⟨ Fact `3 + 1 = 4` ⟩
